</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[874,968,367,392]" pageId="26" pageNumber="227" rank="species">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[874,968,367,392]" pageId="26" pageNumber="227">sp. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
, but differs as follows: postocellar seta absent; bm-cu in line with CuA 
<number box="[503,511,419,433]" pageId="26" pageNumber="227" value="2.0">2</number>
; postgonite, aedeagus, and associated structures narrow and directed posteriorly.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
